of the API surface will be. This is likely to happen after the August 27 WG
Meeting &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://www.w3.org/2011/04/webrtc/wiki/August_27_2024"&gt;https://www.w3.org/2011/04/webrtc/wiki/August_27_2024&lt;/a&gt;&gt;, where this
