&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt; Re the 2nd and the 3rd points, I've added a &quot;Future Work
&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://docs.google.com/document/d/1LjxHl32fE4tCKugrK_PIso7mfXQVEeoD1wSnX2y0ZU8/edit?pli=1&amp;resourcekey=0-d1gP4X2sG7GPl9mlTeptIA&amp;tab=t.0#heading=h.4685f6p8tio9"&gt;https://docs.google.com/document/d/1LjxHl32fE4tCKugrK_PIso7mfXQVEeoD1wSnX2y0ZU8/edit?pli=1&amp;resourcekey=0-d1gP4X2sG7GPl9mlTeptIA&amp;tab=t.0#heading=h.4685f6p8tio9&lt;/a&gt;&gt;&quot;
&gt;&gt; section to the document to capture what I have in mind and what should be
&gt;&gt; done next. Thanks for the suggestion!
&gt;&gt; I've also removed some outdated content from the document like &quot;(TBD)
&gt;&gt; Remove the Scheme Registry&quot;.
