&lt;span class="date"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=date:20240821" rel="nofollow"&gt;Wed, 21 Aug 2024 10:48:18 -0700&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
