&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; On Friday, January 5, 2024 at 7:25:28 PM UTC+1 Francis McCabe wrote:
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; This is an update to the previous intent-to-experiment (filled out a
