&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; permission. 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; There are only manual WPTs for the success scenarios as they involve 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; operating-system-specific share sheets, and external applications to 
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; receive share requests.
